00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:34.296
So they were then able to tell

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:39.656
that both wetsuits were bought
by the same customer at the same time,

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:42.136
October 7, 2014,

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:44.760
in the French city of Calais
by the English Channel.

00:01:45.760 --> 00:01:48.936
But this was all
they were able to figure out.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:50.616
The customer paid cash.

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:53.256
There was no surveillance
footage from the shop.

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:54.760
So it became a cold case.

